00:42:25.160 --> 00:42:26.930
going to make our
economy fiscally

00:42:26.930 --> 00:42:28.720
sound and more efficient.

00:42:28.720 --> 00:42:31.550
And in the long run we all
benefit from that.

00:42:31.550 --> 00:42:33.410
So the government's, by the
way, not proposing that

00:42:33.410 --> 00:42:36.300
today's retirees are hurt,
saying starting in 20 years

00:42:36.300 --> 00:42:37.815
you have to work two
years longer.

00:42:37.815 --> 00:42:41.100
So overall everyone's going to
benefit, but the bottom line

