00:44:06.040 --> 00:44:08.210
They are like same thing,
whatever, but they're higher

00:44:08.210 --> 00:44:09.390
classmen than you, they
have more money,

00:44:09.390 --> 00:44:11.340
they give me the money.

00:44:11.340 --> 00:44:14.560
I take their $3, I pocket $1.

00:44:14.560 --> 00:44:17.210
I come back on Wednesday
and give you each $2.

00:44:17.210 --> 00:44:18.730
You're like, holy shit,
that worked.

00:44:18.730 --> 00:44:20.710
I'm like, I've got a better
deal for you.

00:44:20.710 --> 00:44:24.610
You guys give me $6 and next
time I see you in class--

00:44:24.610 --> 00:44:26.160
semester's ending, but
you get the point--

00:44:26.160 --> 00:44:27.900
I'll give you $10.

00:44:27.900 --> 00:44:29.790
You're like, great, this guy's
trustworthy, we'll do that.

00:44:29.790 --> 00:44:30.880
You give me the $6.

00:44:30.880 --> 00:44:31.650
I pocket $1,

00:44:31.650 --> 00:44:35.080
I go back to my 14.41 and say
